Requirements:
R-Physics for ball
R-Mouse detection
R-Collision for ball with objects
R-Collision for ball with screen boundaries
O-Able to handle change in resolutions mid game
O-Able to handle user unplugging mouse
O-Able to handle user drawing out of bounds
O-Able to handle if user draws on top of ball
O-Works for multiple OS's

O - optional, R - required
